    "IntroductionEnterprise Resource Planning (ERP) systems are integral to modern organizations, streamlining operations across various departments.",
    "Resource allocation within these systems panning human resources, materials, and equipment is a pivotal process that impacts operational efficiency.",
    "Traditional resource allocation models, however, are often rigid and struggle to adapt to fluctuating demands and priorities.",
    "The advent of Machine Learning (ML) has paved the way for more adaptive and intelligent systems.",
    "Reinforcement learning (RL), a subset of ML, offers the potential to dynamically allocate resources based on real-time data and evolving business needs."
  ],
